          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">P<hi rend="small-caps">OOR</hi> ladies! tho' their <hi rend="italics">bus'ness</hi> be to <hi rend="italics">play</hi>,</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-2" n="2">'Tis hard they must be busy <hi rend="italics">night</hi> and <hi rend="italics">day</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-3" n="3">Why shou'd they want the privilege of men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-4" n="4">And take some small <hi rend="italics">diversions</hi>, now and then?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-5" n="5">Had women been the makers of our laws,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-6" n="6">(And why they were not, I can see no cause)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-7" n="7">The men shou'd <hi rend="italics">slave</hi> at <hi rend="italics">cards</hi> from morn to night,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-37L1-line-8" n="8">And female pleasure be to <hi rend="italics">read</hi> and <hi rend="italics">write</hi>.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
